    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<html><head></head><body><h1 id="手动切换Mac-显卡"><a href="#手动切换Mac-显卡" class="headerlink" title="手动切换Mac 显卡"></a>手动切换Mac 显卡</h1><p>主力电脑是一台15年的MacBook Pro 15寸顶配，有的时候，某些程序在运行时系统会把图形卡模式自动调整为高性能，就觉得对性能有影响，想手动切换。<br>系统自带的切换只能选择自动和独显，所以要使用其他方法<br><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GilesWong/GilesWong.github.io@latest/images/pwr.png" alt="" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GilesWong/GilesWong.github.io@latest/images/pwr.png"></p><h3 id="终端切换"><a href="#终端切换" class="headerlink" title="终端切换"></a>终端切换</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">强制使用核显(集成显卡)</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pmset -a GPUSwitch 0</span><br><span class="line">强制使用独立显卡</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pmset -a GPUSwitch 1</span><br><span class="line">自动切换</span><br><span class="line">$ sudo pmset -a GPUSwitch 2</span><br><span class="line">查看是否切换成功</span><br><span class="line">$ pmset -g</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure><p><img src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GilesWong/GilesWong.github.io@latest/images/ter.png" alt="" data-src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/GilesWong/GilesWong.github.io@latest/images/ter.png"></p><h3 id="使用第三方软件"><a href="#使用第三方软件" class="headerlink" title="使用第三方软件"></a>使用第三方软件</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tbody><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">Homebrew 安装 gfxCardStatus</span><br><span class="line">$ brew cask install gfxCardStatus</span><br></pre></td></tr></tbody></table></figure></body></html>]]></content>
    
